short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Simple and unofficial extension used to display the rank of some NFT within collections on the NFT platform of crypto.com.
short.fr: Extension non officielle utilisée pour afficher le rang de certains NFT de collections sur plateforme NFT de crypto.com.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Supported collections:
* PsychoKitties
* Loaded Lions
* AlphaBot
* BeatHeadz
* PsychoMolly
* Ballie
* ArmoryWeapon
* MadHare

Absolutely not required. However, will be accepted as a token of appreciation.
